===============Array Partition=============
class Solution {
    public int arrayPairSum(int[] nums) {
        Arrays.sort(nums);  // Sort the array
        int sum = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < nums.length; i += 2) {
            sum += nums[i]; // Take every even index
        }
        return sum;
    }
}

Example 1:
Input: nums = [1,4,3,2]
Output: 4
